  "description": "Nova-Life is a simulation video game mainly focused on city roleplay in an open world.THE FIRST FRENCH ROLEPLAY GAME!\nIn Nova-Life you can create your own character, find a job and go to work to gain money.\n\nThe Nova-Life project will have around ten dozen or so jobs in its final version, including the possibility of becoming a self-entrepreneur in order to create your own store, and/or your own company which will offer a wide range of choices in the roleplay.\n\nThe roleplay of Nova-Life is a French roleplay. Features • A pleasant driving system\n\n• Written communication and VO-IP\n\n• Multiple vehicles\n\n• Many professions\n\n The jobs have a level hierarchy, which allows you to get a rank in your job and therefore increase your salary",
  "description_short": "Nova-Life: Amboise is a multiplayer role-play simulation video game. Create your character and start your second life!",
